 The morphological Part-of-Speech dictionary and synthesizer 
 used in the Portuguese project is a Freeling Portuguese 
 Linguistic Data conversion. 
 More information about Freeling and licenses can be found 
 http://nlp.lsi.upc.edu/freeling/node/12
 
 Data for Portuguese WordNet [used in Freeling] are extracted 
 from brazilian-wn  project. It is distributed under its original 
 CC-BY license  http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0

